data.title: Grattan Bridge
data.meta_description: Grattan Bridge (Irish: Droichead Grattan) is a road bridge spanning the River Liffey in Dublin, Ireland, and joining Capel Street to Parliament Street and the south quays. #Bridge #Capel_Street #city #crossing #Dublin #Liffey #river #traffic #urban
